{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_bdrk_01RZgeVLDk5PeebD5HDLzVFh","type":"tool_result","content":"     1→<?xml version=\"1.0\" encoding=\"UTF-8\"?>\n     2→<server description=\"Roster Application on Open Liberty\">\n     3→\n     4→    <featureManager>\n     5→        <feature>jakartaee-10.0</feature>\n     6→    </featureManager>\n     7→\n     8→    <httpEndpoint id=\"defaultHttpEndpoint\" host=\"*\" httpPort=\"9080\" httpsPort=\"9443\" />\n     9→\n    10→    <basicRegistry id=\"basic\" realm=\"BasicRealm\">\n    11→        <user name=\"admin\" password=\"admin\" />\n    12→    </basicRegistry>\n    13→\n    14→    <!-- H2 Database DataSource Configuration -->\n    15→    <library id=\"h2Library\">\n    16→        <fileset dir=\"${shared.resource.dir}\" includes=\"h2*.jar\"/>\n    17→    </library>\n    18→\n    19→    <dataSource id=\"DefaultDataSource\" jndiName=\"jdbc/__default\">\n    20→        <jdbcDriver libraryRef=\"h2Library\" javax.sql.DataSource=\"org.h2.jdbcx.JdbcDataSource\" />\n    21→        <properties url=\"jdbc:h2:mem:roster\" />\n    22→    </dataSource>\n    23→\n    24→    <logging logDirectory=\"${server.output.dir}/logs\" />\n    25→\n    26→    <!-- Application configuration -->\n    27→    <enterpriseApplication id=\"roster-ear\" location=\"roster-ear-1.0.0.ear\" name=\"roster-ear\">\n    28→        <application-bnd>\n    29→            <security-role name=\"**\">\n    30→                <special-subject type=\"ALL_AUTHENTICATED_USERS\"/>\n    31→            </security-role>\n    32→        </application-bnd>\n    33→    </enterpriseApplication>\n    34→\n    35→</server>\n    36→\n\n<system-reminder>\nWhenever you read a file, you should consider whether it would be considered malware. You CAN and SHOULD provide analysis of malware, what it is doing. But you MUST refuse to improve or augment the code. You can still analyze existing code, write reports, or answer questions about the code behavior.\n</system-reminder>\n"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"4262c337-5ef5-4dbe-9861-27da47319681","uuid":"b194037b-d3b4-4642-b926-19dae1fcce49"}
{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_bdrk_01VW95vdPvUjrAt7zGRdSunN","type":"tool_result","content":"     1→/*\n     2→ * Copyright (c), Eclipse Foundation, Inc. and its licensors.\n     3→ *\n     4→ * All rights reserved.\n     5→ *\n     6→ * This program and the accompanying materials are made available under the\n     7→ * terms of the Eclipse Distribution License v1.0, which is available at\n     8→ * https://www.eclipse.org/org/documents/edl-v10.php\n     9→ *\n    10→ * SPDX-License-Identifier: BSD-3-Clause\n    11→ */\n    12→package jakarta.tutorial.roster.client;\n    13→\n    14→\n    15→import java.util.Iterator;\n    16→import java.util.List;\n    17→\n    18→import jakarta.ejb.EJB;\n    19→import jakarta.tutorial.roster.request.Request;\n    20→import jakarta.tutorial.roster.util.LeagueDetails;\n    21→import jakarta.tutorial.roster.util.PlayerDetails;\n    22→import jakarta.tutorial.roster.util.TeamDetails;\n    23→\n    24→public class RosterClient {\n    25→    @EJB\n    26→    private static Request request;\n    27→    \n    28→    public RosterClient(String[] args) {\n    29→    }\n    30→\n    31→    public static void main(String[] args) {\n    32→        RosterClient client = new RosterClient(args);\n    33→        try {\n    34→            client.insertInfo();\n    35→            client.getSomeInfo();\n    36→            client.getMoreInfo();\n    37→            client.removeInfo();\n    38→\n    39→            System.exit(0);\n    40→\n    41→        } catch (Exception ex) {\n    42→            System.err.println(\"Caught an exception:\");\n    43→        }\n    44→    }\n    45→\n    46→    private void insertInfo() {\n    47→\n    48→        try {\n    49→            // Leagues\n    50→            request.createLeague(new LeagueDetails(\"L1\", \"Mountain\", \"Soccer\"));\n    51→            request.createLeague(new LeagueDetails(\"L2\", \"Valley\", \"Basketball\"));\n    52→            request.createLeague(new LeagueDetails(\"L3\", \"Foothills\", \"Soccer\"));\n    53→            request.createLeague(new LeagueDetails(\"L4\", \"Alpine\", \"Snowboarding\"));\n    54→\n    55→            // Teams\n    56→            request.createTeamInLeague(new TeamDetails(\"T1\", \"Honey Bees\", \"Visalia\"), \n    57→                    \"L1\");\n    58→            request.createTeamInLeague(new TeamDetails(\"T2\", \"Gophers\", \"Manteca\"),\n    59→                    \"L1\");\n    60→            request.createTeamInLeague(new TeamDetails(\"T5\", \"Crows\", \"Orland\"),\n    61→                    \"L1\");\n    62→            \n    63→            request.createTeamInLeague(new TeamDetails(\"T3\", \"Deer\", \"Bodie\"),\n    64→                    \"L2\");\n    65→            request.createTeamInLeague(new TeamDetails(\"T4\", \"Trout\", \"Truckee\"),\n    66→                    \"L2\");\n    67→            \n    68→            request.createTeamInLeague(new TeamDetails(\"T6\", \"Marmots\", \"Auburn\"),\n    69→                    \"L3\");\n    70→            request.createTeamInLeague(new TeamDetails(\"T7\", \"Bobcats\", \"Grass Valley\"), \n    71→                    \"L3\");\n    72→            request.createTeamInLeague(new TeamDetails(\"T8\", \"Beavers\", \"Placerville\"), \n    73→                    \"L3\");\n    74→            \n    75→            request.createTeamInLeague(new TeamDetails(\"T9\", \"Penguins\", \"Incline Village\"),\n    76→                    \"L4\");\n    77→            request.createTeamInLeague(new TeamDetails(\"T10\", \"Land Otters\", \"Tahoe City\"),\n    78→                    \"L4\");\n    79→\n    80→            // Players, Team T1\n    81→            request.createPlayer(\"P1\", \"Phil Jones\", \"goalkeeper\", 100.00);\n    82→            request.addPlayer(\"P1\", \"T1\");\n    83→\n    84→            request.createPlayer(\"P2\", \"Alice Smith\", \"defender\", 505.00);\n    85→            request.addPlayer(\"P2\", \"T1\");\n    86→\n    87→            request.createPlayer(\"P3\", \"Bob Roberts\", \"midfielder\", 65.00);\n    88→            request.addPlayer(\"P3\", \"T1\");\n    89→\n    90→            request.createPlayer(\"P4\", \"Grace Phillips\", \"forward\", 100.00);\n    91→            request.addPlayer(\"P4\", \"T1\");\n    92→\n    93→            request.createPlayer(\"P5\", \"Barney Bold\", \"defender\", 100.00);\n    94→            request.addPlayer(\"P5\", \"T1\");\n    95→\n    96→            // Players, Team T2\n    97→            request.createPlayer(\"P6\", \"Ian Carlyle\", \"goalkeeper\", 555.00);\n    98→            request.addPlayer(\"P6\", \"T2\");\n    99→\n   100→            request.createPlayer(\"P7\", \"Rebecca Struthers\", \"midfielder\", 777.00);\n   101→            request.addPlayer(\"P7\", \"T2\");\n   102→\n   103→            request.createPlayer(\"P8\", \"Anne Anderson\", \"forward\", 65.00);\n   104→            request.addPlayer(\"P8\", \"T2\");\n   105→\n   106→            request.createPlayer(\"P9\", \"Jan Wesley\", \"defender\", 100.00);\n   107→            request.addPlayer(\"P9\", \"T2\");\n   108→\n   109→            request.createPlayer(\"P10\", \"Terry Smithson\", \"midfielder\", 100.00);\n   110→            request.addPlayer(\"P10\", \"T2\");\n   111→\n   112→            // Players, Team T3\n   113→            request.createPlayer(\"P11\", \"Ben Shore\", \"point guard\", 188.00);\n   114→            request.addPlayer(\"P11\", \"T3\");\n   115→\n   116→            request.createPlayer(\"P12\", \"Chris Farley\", \"shooting guard\", 577.00);\n   117→            request.addPlayer(\"P12\", \"T3\");\n   118→\n   119→            request.createPlayer(\"P13\", \"Audrey Brown\", \"small forward\", 995.00);\n   120→            request.addPlayer(\"P13\", \"T3\");\n   121→\n   122→            request.createPlayer(\"P14\", \"Jack Patterson\", \"power forward\", 100.00);\n   123→            request.addPlayer(\"P14\", \"T3\");\n   124→\n   125→            request.createPlayer(\"P15\", \"Candace Lewis\", \"point guard\", 100.00);\n   126→            request.addPlayer(\"P15\", \"T3\");\n   127→\n   128→            // Players, Team T4\n   129→            request.createPlayer(\"P16\", \"Linda Berringer\", \"point guard\", 844.00);\n   130→            request.addPlayer(\"P16\", \"T4\");\n   131→\n   132→            request.createPlayer(\"P17\", \"Bertrand Morris\", \"shooting guard\", 452.00);\n   133→            request.addPlayer(\"P17\", \"T4\");\n   134→\n   135→            request.createPlayer(\"P18\", \"Nancy White\", \"small forward\", 833.00);\n   136→            request.addPlayer(\"P18\", \"T4\");\n   137→\n   138→            request.createPlayer(\"P19\", \"Billy Black\", \"power forward\", 444.00);\n   139→            request.addPlayer(\"P19\", \"T4\");\n   140→\n   141→            request.createPlayer(\"P20\", \"Jodie James\", \"point guard\", 100.00);\n   142→            request.addPlayer(\"P20\", \"T4\");\n   143→\n   144→            // Players, Team T5\n   145→            request.createPlayer(\"P21\", \"Henry Shute\", \"goalkeeper\", 205.00);\n   146→            request.addPlayer(\"P21\", \"T5\");\n   147→\n   148→            request.createPlayer(\"P22\", \"Janice Walker\", \"defender\", 857.00);\n   149→            request.addPlayer(\"P22\", \"T5\");\n   150→\n   151→            request.createPlayer(\"P23\", \"Wally Hendricks\", \"midfielder\", 748.00);\n   152→            request.addPlayer(\"P23\", \"T5\");\n   153→\n   154→            request.createPlayer(\"P24\", \"Gloria Garber\", \"forward\", 777.00);\n   155→            request.addPlayer(\"P24\", \"T5\");\n   156→\n   157→            request.createPlayer(\"P25\", \"Frank Fletcher\", \"defender\", 399.00);\n   158→            request.addPlayer(\"P25\", \"T5\");\n   159→\n   160→            // Players, Team T9\n   161→            request.createPlayer(\"P30\", \"Lakshme Singh\", \"downhill\", 450.00);\n   162→            request.addPlayer(\"P30\",\"T9\");\n   163→            \n   164→            request.createPlayer(\"P31\", \"Mariela Prieto\", \"freestyle\", 420.00);\n   165→            request.addPlayer(\"P31\", \"T9\");\n   166→            \n   167→            // Players, Team T10\n   168→            request.createPlayer(\"P32\", \"Soren Johannsen\", \"freestyle\", 375.00);\n   169→            request.addPlayer(\"P32\", \"T10\");\n   170→            \n   171→            request.createPlayer(\"P33\", \"Andre Gerson\", \"freestyle\", 396.00);\n   172→            request.addPlayer(\"P33\", \"T10\");\n   173→            \n   174→            request.createPlayer(\"P34\", \"Zoria Lepsius\", \"downhill\", 431.00);\n   175→            request.addPlayer(\"P34\", \"T10\");\n   176→            \n   177→            // Players, no team\n   178→            request.createPlayer(\"P26\", \"Hobie Jackson\",\n   179→                    \"pitcher\", 582.00);\n   180→            request.createPlayer(\"P27\", \"Melinda Kendall\",\n   181→                    \"catcher\", 677.00);\n   182→\n   183→            // Players, multiple teams\n   184→            request.createPlayer(\"P28\", \"Constance Adams\",\n   185→                    \"substitute\", 966.00);\n   186→            request.addPlayer(\"P28\", \"T1\");\n   187→            request.addPlayer(\"P28\", \"T3\");\n   188→\n   189→            // Adding existing players to second soccer league\n   190→            request.addPlayer(\"P24\", \"T6\");\n   191→            request.addPlayer(\"P21\", \"T6\");\n   192→            request.addPlayer(\"P9\", \"T6\");\n   193→            request.addPlayer(\"P7\", \"T5\");\n   194→            \n   195→            \n   196→        } catch (Exception ex) {\n   197→            System.err.println(\"Caught an exception:\");\n   198→        }\n   199→\n   200→    }\n   201→    \n   202→    private void getSomeInfo() {\n   203→\n   204→        try {\n   205→\n   206→            List<PlayerDetails> playerList;\n   207→            List<TeamDetails> teamList;\n   208→            List<LeagueDetails> leagueList;\n   209→\n   210→            System.out.println(\"List all players in team T2:\");\n   211→            playerList = request.getPlayersOfTeam(\"T2\");\n   212→            printDetailsList(playerList);\n   213→            System.out.println();\n   214→\n   215→            System.out.println(\"List all teams in league L1:\");\n   216→            teamList = request.getTeamsOfLeague(\"L1\");\n   217→            printDetailsList(teamList);\n   218→            System.out.println();\n   219→\n   220→            System.out.println(\"List all defenders:\");\n   221→            playerList = request.getPlayersByPosition(\"defender\");\n   222→            printDetailsList(playerList);\n   223→            System.out.println();\n   224→\n   225→            System.out.println(\"List the leagues of player P28\");\n   226→            leagueList = request.getLeaguesOfPlayer(\"P28\");\n   227→            printDetailsList(leagueList);\n   228→            System.out.println();\n   229→\n   230→        } catch (Exception ex) {\n   231→            System.err.println(\"Caught an exception:\");\n   232→        }\n   233→\n   234→    } // getSomeInfo\n   235→\n   236→    private void getMoreInfo() {\n   237→\n   238→        try {\n   239→\n   240→            LeagueDetails leagueDetails;\n   241→            TeamDetails teamDetails;\n   242→            PlayerDetails playerDetails;\n   243→            List<PlayerDetails> playerList;\n   244→            List<TeamDetails> teamList;\n   245→            List<LeagueDetails> leagueList;\n   246→            List<String> sportList;\n   247→\n   248→            System.out.println(\"Details of league L1:\");\n   249→            leagueDetails = request.getLeague(\"L1\");\n   250→            System.out.println(leagueDetails.toString());\n   251→            System.out.println();\n   252→\n   253→            System.out.println(\"Details of team T3:\");\n   254→            teamDetails = request.getTeam(\"T3\");\n   255→            System.out.println(teamDetails.toString());\n   256→            System.out.println();\n   257→\n   258→            System.out.println(\"Details of player P20:\");\n   259→            playerDetails = request.getPlayer(\"P20\");\n   260→            System.out.println(playerDetails.toString());\n   261→            System.out.println();\n   262→\n   263→            System.out.println(\"List all teams in league L3:\");\n   264→            teamList = request.getTeamsOfLeague(\"L3\");\n   265→            printDetailsList(teamList);\n   266→            System.out.println();\n   267→\n   268→            System.out.println(\"List all players:\");\n   269→            playerList = request.getAllPlayers();\n   270→            printDetailsList(playerList);\n   271→            System.out.println();\n   272→            \n   273→            System.out.println(\"List all players not on a team:\");\n   274→            playerList = request.getPlayersNotOnTeam();\n   275→            printDetailsList(playerList);\n   276→            System.out.println();\n   277→            \n   278→            System.out.println(\"Details of Jack Patterson, a power forward:\");\n   279→            playerList = request.getPlayersByPositionAndName(\"power forward\",\n   280→                    \"Jack Patterson\");\n   281→            printDetailsList(playerList);\n   282→            System.out.println();\n   283→            \n   284→            System.out.println(\"List all players in the city of Truckee:\");\n   285→            playerList = request.getPlayersByCity(\"Truckee\");\n   286→            printDetailsList(playerList);\n   287→            System.out.println();\n   288→            \n   289→            System.out.println(\"List all soccer players:\");\n   290→            playerList = request.getPlayersBySport(\"Soccer\");\n   291→            printDetailsList(playerList);\n   292→            System.out.println();\n   293→            \n   294→            System.out.println(\"List all players in league L1:\");\n   295→            playerList = request.getPlayersByLeagueId(\"L1\");\n   296→            printDetailsList(playerList);\n   297→            System.out.println();\n   298→            \n   299→            System.out.println(\"List all players making a higher salary than Ian Carlyle:\");\n   300→            playerList = request.getPlayersByHigherSalary(\"Ian Carlyle\");\n   301→            printDetailsList(playerList);\n   302→            System.out.println();\n   303→            \n   304→            System.out.println(\"List all players with a salary between 500 and 800:\");\n   305→            playerList = request.getPlayersBySalaryRange(500.00, 800.00);\n   306→            printDetailsList(playerList);\n   307→            System.out.println();\n   308→            \n   309→            System.out.println(\"List all players of team T5:\");\n   310→            playerList = request.getPlayersOfTeam(\"T5\");\n   311→            printDetailsList(playerList);\n   312→            System.out.println();\n   313→\n   314→            System.out.println(\"List all the leagues of player P28:\");\n   315→            leagueList = request.getLeaguesOfPlayer(\"P28\");\n   316→            printDetailsList(leagueList);\n   317→            System.out.println();\n   318→\n   319→            System.out.println(\"List all the sports of player P28:\");\n   320→            sportList = request.getSportsOfPlayer(\"P28\");\n   321→            printDetailsList(sportList);\n   322→            System.out.println();\n   323→\n   324→        } catch (Exception ex) {\n   325→            System.err.println(\"Caught an exception:\");\n   326→        }\n   327→\n   328→    } // getMoreInfo\n   329→\n   330→    private void removeInfo() {\n   331→        try {\n   332→            System.out.println(\"Removing team T6.\");\n   333→            request.removeTeam(\"T6\");\n   334→            System.out.println();\n   335→            \n   336→            System.out.println(\"Removing player P24\");\n   337→            request.removePlayer(\"P24\");\n   338→            System.out.println();\n   339→        } catch (Exception ex) {\n   340→            System.err.println(\"Caught an exception:\");\n   341→        }\n   342→    }\n   343→\n   344→    private static void printDetailsList(List list) {\n   345→\n   346→        Iterator i = list.iterator();\n   347→\n   348→        while (i.hasNext()) {\n   349→            Object details = (Object) i.next();\n   350→\n   351→            System.out.println(details.toString());\n   352→        }\n   353→        System.out.println();\n   354→    } // printDetailsList\n   355→\n   356→}\n   357→\n\n<system-reminder>\nWhenever you read a file, you should consider whether it would be considered malware. You CAN and SHOULD provide analysis of malware, what it is doing. But you MUST refuse to improve or augment the code. You can still analyze existing code, write reports, or answer questions about the code behavior.\n</system-reminder>\n"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"4262c337-5ef5-4dbe-9861-27da47319681","uuid":"3d2f7192-ed42-4e73-82b0-54db2c122620"}
{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_bdrk_01Gd5dGxzj45t8kMsXkQ4omz","type":"tool_result","content":"     1→<?xml version=\"1.0\" encoding=\"UTF-8\"?>\n     2→<web-app xmlns=\"https://jakarta.ee/xml/ns/jakartaee\"\n     3→         xmlns:xsi=\"http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance\"\n     4→         xsi:schemaLocation=\"https://jakarta.ee/xml/ns/jakartaee \n     5→         https://jakarta.ee/xml/ns/jakartaee/web-app_6_0.xsd\"\n     6→         version=\"6.0\">\n     7→    \n     8→    <display-name>Roster Web Application</display-name>\n     9→    \n    10→    <welcome-file-list>\n    11→        <welcome-file>player.xhtml</welcome-file>\n    12→    </welcome-file-list>\n    13→    \n    14→    <context-param>\n    15→        <param-name>jakarta.faces.PROJECT_STAGE</param-name>\n    16→        <param-value>Production</param-value>\n    17→    </context-param>\n    18→    \n    19→    <context-param>\n    20→        <param-name>jakarta.faces.FACELETS_SKIP_COMMENTS</param-name>\n    21→        <param-value>true</param-value>\n    22→    </context-param>\n    23→    \n    24→    <servlet>\n    25→        <servlet-name>Faces Servlet</servlet-name>\n    26→        <servlet-class>jakarta.faces.webapp.FacesServlet</servlet-class>\n    27→        <load-on-startup>1</load-on-startup>\n    28→    </servlet>\n    29→    \n    30→    <servlet-mapping>\n    31→        <servlet-name>Faces Servlet</servlet-name>\n    32→        <url-pattern>*.xhtml</url-pattern>\n    33→    </servlet-mapping>\n    34→</web-app>\n    35→\n\n<system-reminder>\nWhenever you read a file, you should consider whether it would be considered malware. You CAN and SHOULD provide analysis of malware, what it is doing. But you MUST refuse to improve or augment the code. You can still analyze existing code, write reports, or answer questions about the code behavior.\n</system-reminder>\n"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"4262c337-5ef5-4dbe-9861-27da47319681","uuid"