ta EE with single-module Spring Boot 3.2.5\n- Dockerfile: Updated build and run commands for Spring Boot JAR\n- .dockerignore: Updated to exclude old module directories\n\nRetained (unchanged, superseded by new src/ layout):\n- roster-common/: Old module (excluded from Docker build)\n- roster-ejb/: Old module (excluded from Docker build)\n- roster-web/: Old module (excluded from Docker build)\n- roster-ear/: Old module (excluded from Docker build)\n- roster-appclient/: Old module (excluded from Docker build)\n```\n\n### Step-by-Step Log\n\n```\n[2026-03-17T00:00:00Z] [info] Analyzed project: 5-module Jakarta EE 10 app on Open Liberty\n[2026-03-17T00:01:00Z] [info] Planned migration strategy: consolidate to Spring Boot 3.2.5\n[2026-03-17T00:02:00Z] [info] Created single-module project structure\n[2026-03-17T00:03:00Z] [info] Updated pom.xml with Spring Boot dependencies\n[2026-03-17T00:04:00Z] [info] Migrated 5 JPA entity classes with field-based annotations\n[2026-03-17T00:05:00Z] [info] Migrated 4 DTO/util classes\n[2026-03-17T00:06:00Z] [info] Converted EJB RequestBean to Spring @Service\n[2026-03-17T00:07:00Z] [info] Converted EJB DataInitializer to Spring CommandLineRunner\n[2026-03-17T00:08:00Z] [info] Converted JAX-RS RosterResource to Spring @RestController\n[2026-03-17T00:09:00Z] [info] Created application.properties for H2 + JPA\n[2026-03-17T00:10:00Z] [info] Created Spring Boot RosterApplication entry point\n[2026-03-17T00:11:00Z] [info] Updated Dockerfile and .dockerignore\n[2026-03-17T00:12:00Z] [info] Created smoke.py with 22 test cases\n[2026-03-17T00:13:00Z] [info] Docker build succeeded\n[2026-03-17T00:14:00Z] [info] Application started successfully (port 34339)\n[2026-03-17T00:15:00Z] [info] All 22 smoke tests passed\n[2026-03-17T00:16:00Z] [info] Migration complete\n```\n\n### Error Handling\n\n- **Error Summary:** 0 errors encountered during migration\n- **Critical Issues:** None\n- **All endpoints preserved:** League CRUD, Team CRUD, Player CRUD, all query endpoints, relationship management"}],"stop_reason":"end_turn","stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":568,"cache_read_input_tokens":108189,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":568,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0},"output_tokens":1244},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"4262c337-5ef5-4dbe-9861-27da47319681","uuid":"08d5ddca-05d4-444c-8919-2f42cdc8f3e5"}
